title: US Census, Childern in Poverty by School Districts, USA, 2007
name: US Census, Childern in Poverty by School Districts, USA, 2007
description:
The point shapefile shows number of children in poverty by school district for the year 2007. The estimates for total population, population of children age 5 to 17 and children in poverty was released by Census on Jan 25, 2008. The raw data was joined to point shape file of the school districts for the lower 48 states.  
The data for the school enrollments is from year 2006.
